Package org.sbml.squeezer

This is the core of SBMLsqueezer as it contains the central classes for reaction type analysis, kineticl law generation and some specialized exceptions.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
LawListener Classes that implement this interface can display the progress made by KineticLawGenerator when assigning BasicKineticLaw, Parameter, UnitDefinition objects and so forth to a model.
 

Class Summary
KineticLawGenerator This class identifies and generates the missing kinetic laws for a the selected model in the given plug-in.
ReactionType The purpose of this class is to analyze a reaction object for several properties, such as the number of reactants and products, the types of modifiers and their number, if the stoichiometries are always integer numbers or real valued and much more.
Reflect This class loads other classes that implement certain interfaces or extend certain super types.
Reflect.ClassComparator<T> Compares the string values of given objects.
SBMLsqueezer The main program of SBMLsqueezer.
 

Enum Summary
CfgKeys This is a list of possible command line options and configuration of SBMLsqueezer.
 

Exception Summary
ModificationException An exception that can be raised if a wront type of modification is assigned to a reaction; it is a special kind of a RateLawNotApplicableException.
RateLawNotApplicableException An exception to be thrown if the selected kinetics is not applicable to the given reaction.
 

Package org.sbml.squeezer Description

This is the core of SBMLsqueezer as it contains the central classes for reaction type analysis, kineticl law generation and some specialized exceptions.
